verbose_text: XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR The absence of any significant effects of the plant extract on ethoxyresorufin-O-deethylase activity mediated by CYP1A/1A2 isozymes (XREF_FIG) would suggest that the plant extract would not impair the clearance of drugs that are metabolized by CYP1A/1A2 isozymes.
